org.loboevolution.pdfview.annotation

Class PDFAnnotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.loboevolution.pdfview.annotation.PDFAnnotation
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LinkAnnotation, StampAnnotation, WidgetAnnotation

    public class PDFAnnotation
extends Object
    Encapsulate a PDF annotation. This is only the super-class of PDF annotations, which has an "unknown" annotation type. Use the createAnnotation() method for getting an annotation of the correct type (if implemented). Author Katja Sondermann
    Since:
    03.07.2009
